data.description: Welcome to 230 Townsend Avenue!! As you drive up to this detached single-family home, the first thing you notice is the beautifully maintained fenced-in corner lot. The solid construction red brick exterior adds charm and curb appeal, and invites you in. Enter into an cozy living room / dining room combination that opens to the kitchen. To the left, the master bedroom with walk-in closet, a full bathroom, and guest bedroom with spacious closet. On the other side of the house, you will find a large family room / bonus room. On your way to the attached 2-car garage, you will find a large storage closet and half bathroom. On the rear of the property is a separate unit with a bedroom, bathroom and kitchenette. Great for in-law suite, guest house, or rental property. Beautiful fruit trees in the yard, which is equipped with well irrigation system. You will also find a storage shed and covered carport with additional parking space on the side driveway.
